text: ShopHQ, formerly known as Evine until 2019, is an American cable, satellite and broadcast television network owned by iMedia Brands Inc. The channel is headquartered in Eden Prairie, Minnesota. The home shopping channel's main competitors are Qurate's HSN and QVC. == References == == Other websites == * * iMedia Brands, Inc., corporate website Category:1990s establishments in Minnesota Category:1991 establishments in the United States Category:American television networks Category:Minnesota
